# 64-Bit Unsigned Integer Vectors

**API Collection**

Perform operations on vectors that contain unsigned 64-bit integer elements.

## Vector Data Types

- **simd_ulong1**: A vector of one 64-bit unsigned integer element.
- **simd_ulong2**: A vector of two 64-bit unsigned integer elements.
- **simd_ulong3**: A vector of three 64-bit unsigned integer elements.
- **simd_ulong4**: A vector of four 64-bit unsigned integer elements.
- **simd_ulong8**: A vector of eight 64-bit unsigned integer elements.

## Packed Vector Data Types

- **simd_packed_ulong2**: A packed vector of two 64-bit unsigned integer element.
- **simd_packed_ulong4**: A packed vector of four 64-bit unsigned integer elements.
- **simd_packed_ulong8**: A packed vector of eight 64-bit unsigned integer elements.

## Unsigned Integer Vectors

- **8-Bit Unsigned Integer Vectors**: Perform operations on vectors that contain unsigned 8-bit integer elements.
- **16-Bit Unsigned Integer Vectors**: Perform operations on vectors that contain unsigned 16-bit integer elements.
- **32-Bit Unsigned Integer Vectors**: Perform operations on vectors that contain unsigned 32-bit integer elements.
